Le truc dois être user-friendly.
    Il faut donner des phrase explenatoires qui inclut les functions du truc.


BufferReader is better than Scanner in the sense that it
does not require the type to be consistent when reading from the user.

Use if-else and try-catch statements to handle the errors. No errors should be thrown during the tests.

